{"tid":840832,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"岳飛成世仔被人跣得最金個鑊係咪就係佢老母？","createTime":"2018-09-29T06:10:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T06:59:27.000Z","uid":38539,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"42980bc4fd8857007366eb733d906a08b5e8e2e1","tid":840832,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T06:10:59.000Z","msg":"２０歲的岳飛已經是個飽讀兵書、諳熟武藝、身強力壯的年輕人,他盼望有一天能夠投身疆場, 為國家報仇雪恥．當招募&rdquo;敢戰士&rdquo;的消息傳來時, 他報名參軍．就在他走上戰場的前夕, 深明大義的母親, 特意在他背上刺下&rdquo;精忠報國&rdquo;四個大字, 囑咐他一生一世都要為國家和民族的利益而奮勇殺敵, 決不吝惜自己的生命． <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n岳飛都根本望唔到自己嘅背脊，佢老母剌係佢背脊叮囑佢精忠報國，係咪特登玩鳩個仔？為國家奮鬥，結果被國家處死埋，兩母子都柒吓柒吓..."},{"pid":"b3a044ea9f959ae6df72b9f8a4489f8fdc19fcde","tid":840832,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T06:12:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32a49fb0072eb5ad0c95dde6e541c09cdfc1fd0f","tid":840832,"uid":182334,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T06:32:45.000Z","msg":"潮媽！依家都無幾個人會幫自己的子女紋身"},{"pid":"07828743102143c889a7982bf6717e1a2f2e4eb4","tid":840832,"uid":143260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T06:36:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">岳飛都根本望唔到自己嘅背脊，</span>應該紋身紋胸前面先啱"},{"pid":"205bcc1719846db08748f0c233ef9cecdb7381cb","tid":840832,"uid":143260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07828743102143c889a7982bf6717e1a2f2e4eb4","tid":840832,"uid":143260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T06:36:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">岳飛都根本望唔到自己嘅背脊，</span>應該紋身紋胸前面先啱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T06:36:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843d7d988b43454baa93e52d156e54dee1dd9aa7","tid":840832,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T06:59:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}